#
# #PRE
# #DOM:&lt;domain&gt;
# #INCLUDE &lt;filename&gt;
# #BEGIN_ALTERNATE
# #END_ALTERNATE
# \0xnn (non-printing character support)
#
# Following any entry in the file with the characters "#PRE" will cause
# the entry to be preloaded into the name cache. By default, entries are
